### Tasks

Backend:

- controller: `TaskController`
- service: `TaskService`, `TaskServiceImpl`
- repositories: `TaskRepository`, `TaskLogRepository`
- DTOs: `dto/task/*`
- entities: `Task`, `TaskLog`

Frontend:

- route: `/task`
- page: `prms-web/src/app/pages/management/tasks/task-list/*`
- shared task logic service: `prms-web/src/app/pages/management/tasks/services/task.service.ts`
- models: `prms-web/src/app/pages/management/tasks/models/*`
