Frontend:

- route: `/kanban`
- page: `prms-web/src/app/pages/kanban/task-kanban/*`
- route file: `prms-web/src/app/pages/kanban/kanban.routes.ts`

When task mentions drag/drop board, column status, or project board view, check task service and kanban page together.

### Resource Allocation

