- models: `prms-web/src/app/pages/resource-allocation/models/*`

### App Params

Backend:

- controller: `AppParamController`
- service: `AppParamService`, `AppParamServiceImpl`
- repository: `AppParamRepository`
- entity: `AppParam`

Frontend:

- route: `/management/app-params`
- page: `prms-web/src/app/pages/management/app-params/app-param-list/*`
